ers\", \"from\": 1374, \"to\": 1381}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Asked about her experience with sevens and a possible shot at becoming an Olympian, 20-year-old Corrigan (above) said: \\\"I did underage Sevens and I went to Marcoussis in France a few times and yeah, I like the Sevens but playing now, you got a taste of the 15s and I love that as well.\", \"from\": 1401, \"to\": 1686, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1475, \"end\": 1483, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999994850274068, \"rank\": 5.149730561145879e-07, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 1571, \"end\": 1577, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999982605914, \"rank\": 1.7337286734909413e-09, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her experience\", \"from\": 1413, \"to\": 1427}, {\"ngram\": \"sevens\", \"from\": 1433, \"to\": 1439}, {\"ngram\": \"a possible shot\", \"from\": 1444, \"to\": 1459}, {\"ngram\": \"Sevens\", \"from\": 1536, \"to\": 1542}, {\"ngram\": \"Marcoussis\", \"from\": 1557, \"to\": 1567}, {\"ngram\": \"the Sevens\", \"from\": 1607, \"to\": 1617}, {\"ngram\": \"a taste\", \"from\": 1643, \"to\": 1650}, {\"ngram\": \"the 15s\", \"from\": 1654, \"to\": 1661}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yeah, I do not know.\\\"\", \"from\": 1687, \"to\": 1708, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, one player who has ruled herself out of contention is Brittany Hogan, player of the match in the 15-12 win over the Scots.\", \"from\": 1710, \"to\": 1841, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1773, \"end\": 1787, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miss_California_USA\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\":